# Frontend Inspirations

## 1. AllRecipes (www.allrecipes.com)

Key Features:

- Clean grid layout for recipe cards
- Large, appetizing food images
- Clear category navigation
- Search bar prominently displayed

## 2. Food Network (www.foodnetwork.com)

Standout Elements:

- Hero section with featured recipes
- Seasonal recipe collections
- Professional food photography
- Easy-to-read recipe ratings

## 3. Epicurious (www.epicurious.com)

Design Highlights:

- Minimalist white space usage
- Typography hierarchy
- Interactive recipe filters
- Elegant color scheme

Based on these inspirations, let's enhance our homepage with:

- Large hero section
- Featured recipe grid
- Clean typography
- Professional color scheme
- Clear navigation
